{
  "id": "RAW_4bc70e",
  "title": "腾讯混元 Hunyuan-A13B 技术报告：智能与效率“甜蜜点”的极致追求",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkwODU2OTQyNQ==&mid=2247495064&idx=1&sn=c80794fad5e8b16fbd40fc98c3feb8d3",
  "date": "2025-07-14 12:30:00",
  "author": "腾讯混元",
  "siteName": "腾讯混元",
  "content": "\n \n \n  <p><span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">腾讯混元Hunyuan-A13B已于此前</span><a class=\"normal_text_link\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 217);\" href=\"https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkwODU2OTQyNQ==&amp;mid=2247494977&amp;idx=1&amp;sn=ca8c9dc82eb470ea2f7096ab67339706&amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect\" textvalue=\"正式宣布开源\" data-itemshowtype=\"0\" linktype=\"text\" data-linktype=\"2\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 217);font-style: normal;text-decoration: underline;\">正式宣布开源</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-style: italic;\">,这款大模型如何以百亿参数挑战千亿级模型性能，精准卡位参数规模与智能表现的 Sweet Spot （甜蜜点）？从预训练到后训练，背后都有哪些硬核操作？Agent能力又是如何炼成，让 Hunyuan-A13B 成为撬动 AI 应用落地的关键杠杆？</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><o:p>\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">腾讯混元团队近日正式宣布其最新大语言模型 Hunyuan-80B-A13B（下面简称Hunyuan-A13B）全面开源，</span></span>\n   </o:p><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">模型API在腾讯云官网上线，</span></span><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">输入价格为每百万Tokens 0.5元，输出价格为每百万Tokens 2元。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><o:p>\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这款模型基于领先的混合专家(MoE)架构，模型仅凭百亿级参数的轻量规模，实现了可与业界前沿千亿级模型相媲美的性能，精准击中了长期以来困扰大模型领域的智能与效率的“甜蜜点”。</span></span>\n   </o:p></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><o:p>\n    <span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Hunyuan-A13B的开源，旨在提供一个兼具顶尖性能与低成本部署优势的强大基座，成为撬动AI应用落地的新支点。&nbsp;</span></span>\n   </o:p><o:page></o:page></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.487962962962963\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 604.74px;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=2b8cb314&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9u3YmmgmjbRQE7WIupmHFajByGt7f18wm44AwvEyPhQtwCFI7wsR6QicmLsqibxU68lPHQxokXuyGxUylNSQeJUg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;border-bottom: 3px solid rgb(6, 50, 253);padding-bottom: 3px;border-top-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-right-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-left-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 50, 253);border-top-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-right-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-left-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">为AI普惠应用而生，定义“甜蜜点”</span></span></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <h1 style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">当前大模型应用领域普遍面临一个困境：</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 217);font-weight: bold;\">性能越强的模型往往伴随着更高的部署和推理成本</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。追求极致效果就往往要选择满血版本的大模型，而高昂的推理费用则劝退了不少业务，腾讯混元推出的Hunyuan-A13B，正是为了破解这一难题。</span></span></h1>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">腾讯混元此次开源的Hunyuan-A13B采用了高性能的细粒度MoE(混合专家)架构，总参数规模为800亿，而单次推理仅需激活130亿参数。这种“以小博大”的精巧设计，使其在保持强大智能的同时，推理吞吐量相较同类前沿模型提升超过100%。加之其原生支持的256K超长上下文窗口， Hunyuan-A13B在核心指标上，为业界树立了一个全新的性能与效率平衡的标杆。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">Hunyuan-A13B 模型对个人开发者较为友好，在严格条件下，只需要1张中端GPU卡即可部署。目前，Hunyuan-A13B 全面融入开源生态，支持主流推理框架（i.e. SGLang，vLLM and TensorRT-LLM），无损支持多种量化格式。&nbsp;</span></span><o:page></o:page></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.6472795497185742\" data-w=\"1066\" style=\"width: 604.74px;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=86128606&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9u3YmmgmjbRQE7WIupmHFajByGt7f18wChOdd6OeKCNXqTpu25cjTohrowia4TRXbicgVEaV2vLoTqWgsdJvoyyA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <div style=\"box-sizing: border-box;font-style: normal;font-weight: 400;text-align: justify;font-size: 16px;color: rgb(62, 62, 62);\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;border-bottom: 3px solid rgb(6, 50, 253);padding-bottom: 3px;border-top-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-right-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-left-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(6, 50, 253);border-top-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-right-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);border-left-color: rgb(6, 50, 253);box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 8px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;line-height: 1.5em;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">技术拆解：揭秘“甜蜜点”背后的硬核操作</span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <h1 style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">如此精准卡位的“甜蜜点”是如何炼成的？我们将先揭秘其背后的两大技术支柱：高质量的预训练、结构化的后训练。接着，我们以“Agent能力”构建为样板，拆解SFT与RL双轮驱动的后训练方案设计。</span></span></h1>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">夯实基座苦练内功：高质量预训练</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">高质量的输入是决定模型能力上限的关键。Hunyuan-A13B的高性能背后，离不开腾讯混元团队在预训练阶段对训练数据的精心打磨，团队不只追求数量，更追求质量。</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 217);font-weight: bold;\">模型在高达20T Tokens的优质数据上训练，更关键的是，团队对STEM(科学、技术、工程和数学)领域的数据进行了专项强化，这成为模型在推理任务中表现出色的重要基础</span><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">。同时，通过科学的三阶段训练策略，团队稳步构建并扩展了模型的能力。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">具体来说，这三阶段训练策略包括：</span></span><o:page></o:page></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（1）基础训练阶段， 旨在构建模型的核心语言理解和生成能力，为后续优化奠定坚实基础；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（2）快速退火阶段，通过调整 样本配比和学习率优化，快速提升模型在推理上的性能表现；</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">（3）以及长文本训练阶段，逐步扩展模型的上下文处理能力，最终实现了原生支持256K超长上下文窗口。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这一策略结合了上下文窗口 的扩展，不仅确保能够兼顾学习基础模式和处理长距离依赖，也显著提升了模型的泛化能力。可 以说，强大的基础决定了模型能达到的最终高度。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.4324074074074074\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 604.74px;height: auto !important;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=040a94c5&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2F9u3YmmgmjbRQE7WIupmHFajByGt7f18wjsBSHWg4Gw5RTn1dFaGLUiaeJ5cRiafJy5Q2OrzEbLIiaG2EcicAJXcaEQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-style: normal;font-weight: normal;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 15px;font-weight: bold;\">激发潜能专项优化：结构化后训练</span></span></h3>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;line-height: 1.5em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9);font-size: 17px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,